title: I'm with You by Glenna Maynard
description:
"We're just trying to figure out this life, how to
get from one day to the next. And though we tried,
we've lost it all somehow. But our love won't be
tragic. Just remember I'm with You..."

Bella Rose and Cutter Dawson are two lost souls trying
to find their place in this world. They have known loss.
But with pain comes beauty. When they find each other
in the midst of their darkest hours, will the beauty they
see in each other be enough to save them?



I'm with You
by Glenna Maynard
Language: EN
